<p>
 The Tarrasque:  Resist fire and cold. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Ugluk, the Uruk:  Resist fire, cold, and poison. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Ulfang, the Black:  Resist electricity, fire, and cold; Summon a number of pets. 
</p>
</li>
